        <article><strong>$svg</strong><span>SVG assets</span></article>
      </section>
      <p class="note">Review strategy, prompts, image approvals, SVG manifest, and content-campaign-plan before render.</p>
    </main>
    <style>
      [data-composition-id="brand-campaign-board"] { width: 100%; height: 100%; background: #07111f; color: #e8f3ff; font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif; overflow: hidden; }
